    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ <date>Diem mercurii qui est septimo kalendas aprelis</date>, presentia
                            <rs>bonorum hominum</rs> quorum nomina subter leguntur, in <placeName
                                key="#Villas #Mills #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals" ref="#places/399"><rs key="#Villas">villa</rs>
                            Asspi</placeName> pertinentia <rs key="#Castle">castris</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/145">Nogarie</placeName> per vuasonem
                        terre que in sua tenebat manu, <persName key="#Mills #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #daughterOf"><name ref="Rosa"
                            >Rosa</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#daughterOf">filia</rs> quondam <persName key="faherOf"><name ref="Dominicus"
                            >Dominici</name></persName> investivit <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominicum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiterum</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Mills #Landed_possessions #Wine #Cereals #Priests #Monks" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> po situm inter <rs key="#Rivers">Padum</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rivers">Largionem</rs> ad iura ipsius monasterii de omnibus rebus
                        territoriis iuris sui seu et de parte <rs key="#Mills">molendini</rs> quem
                        habere in <rs key="#Rivers">Tartaro</rs>, tam <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >sediminis</rs> quam <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals">arabilis</rs>, tam in
                        eadem villa Asspi quam in pertinentiis predicti castri seu in <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/59"
                            >Veronese</placeName></geogName>, ita ut faciat exinde a presenti die
                        pars ipsius monasterii aut cuius pars monasterii dederit proprietario nomine
                        quicquid voluerit, sine omni contradictionem predicte Rose suorumque eredum;
                        et si exinde agere aut causare presumpserit ut componat ipsa res <rs>in
                            duplo</rs>. <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ambrosius"
                                >Ambrosius</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Dominicus"
                                    >Dominicus</name></persName> atque <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonacausa"
                                        >Bonacausa</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness #Deacons"><name ref="Albitius"
                                >Albizo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> seu et <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Angnel">Iohannes</name>
                            <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> qui Angnel</persName> vocatur et
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Albitius/dal Casale">Albizo</name> dal
                            Casale</persName> interfuerunt. Factum est hoc <date>anno ab
                            incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi milesimo sexagesimo VIllvo,
                            indictione sexta</date>. </ab>
